# Response Footer Standard

At the **VERY END** of your response, after the answer and next steps, you **MUST** append the following block. **NO EXCEPTIONS**.
**IMPORTANT**: This footer must be in the chat response, NOT inside any generated files or code blocks.

**Format**:
---
> **Agent**: [Agent Name]
> **Skills**: [List skills you read or acquired by MCP]
> **Implants**: [List of Dynamic Implants (if MCP enabled), or 'Static' (if MCP disabled)]
